reviews: A story about two young people who make their living by seducing rich people. When they run into each other, sparks start to fly. Good quality DVD with proper English subtitles. The plot is light, but acting is competent. Beata Tyszkiewicz is excellent. Watch it if you have nothing better to do.

i saw it for the second time today and for the second time it was a pleasure:). nice, nice romantic movie:) not ambitious, but which romantic comedy is so?:).. a good play of good young actors:) young, talented and pretty:) just to spend nice time and to feel happy, watching like others find each other to live long and..:)
